{"tid":125463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】「吃不起別吃」麵檔老闆當街遭斬首 食客丟頭落垃圾桶","createTime":"2017-02-18T13:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T19:43:58.000Z","uid":38376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c79c9b2887c10011beeabda5f175249dfaf7b9a","tid":125463,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:33:22.000Z","msg":"湖北武漢今日中午發生恐怖血案，當地武昌火車站前一個麵檔老闆，疑因價格問題與食客發生爭吵，並發生肢體衝突，食客突然拿起菜刀，將老闆的頭顱斬下，扔到垃圾桶。警方將這名疑犯拘捕，將案件定性為故意殺人案，正在調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，食客到麵檔吃過3碗麵後，因每碗麵一元錢的差價食客與老闆發生爭執。有圍觀者稱，發生爭執後，食客問為何3碗麵會這麼貴，老闆竟說：「吃不起別吃！」食客便拿起菜刀，向老闆狂斬。<br />\n<br />\n事後警方將兇手拘捕，斬人者姓胡，22歲，死者姓姚，42歲，來自湖北十堰人，在武漢經營麵館一年左右。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現場片段，恐怖慎入<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iiCG0Gm63pc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiiCG0Gm63pc&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=eaf5c0bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iiCG0Gm63pc</a>"},{"pid":"4ce9bd27ba89122fe2f1c9440680802128931893","tid":125463,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:19:32.000Z","msg":"點解食客隨身有菜刀.同埋點解可以無人阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4753be6558f7f24bb754a9f98ee6d03e43262714","tid":125463,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:24:21.000Z","msg":"條片無左"},{"pid":"9002bbd22345fae74db40c7cf07921722fe26907","tid":125463,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解食客隨身有菜刀.同埋點解可以無人阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好明顯拎麵檔嗰啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfc1a1408dd3aee23cf1cfe99155a28371b8f69","tid":125463,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條片無左</blockquote><br />\n有冇backup?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"